title: #98: The Conspiracy Farm With Pat Miletich and Jeffery Wilson
description: Thank you for tuning into another fun episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. Today the boys welcome Pat Miletich and Jeffery Wilson from the Conspiracy Farm podcast to discuss the RICO case against Harvey Weinstein and FRIENDS!!!!  Please check out all of our new t-shirts we have available at AllComedyTshirts.com.  Also you can support the show at Patreon.com/TinFoilHat!
